title: 2U Rack Shelf,19 inch Server Rack Shelf 12 inch Depth,Weight Capacity 110Lbs/50kg,Rack Mount Shelf for 19" Network Racks & Cabinets,with Complete Accessories

Available in 12", 14", 16" depth ,1 and 2 pack,Meet different needs.
